When checked you can map field from the Graph API (/me endpoint) to field names in the user. These values get synced every login.
When disabled the link to the Office login will be shown on the bottom of the login form.

When enabled anonymous users that access the /user/login page will automatically be redirected to the SSO login page. Users that use "local" users (like admins) can use the /user/drupal_login path to use the normal Drupal login.
When enabled nog login form will be shown. This can be overridden with ?show_login=true query parameter.
